00:07:10.388 --> 00:07:12.182 position:50% align:center
[SAWAKI]
Running?

00:07:12.265 --> 00:07:14.434 position:50% align:center
Um...

00:07:21.816 --> 00:07:23.985 position:50% align:center
Ohto.

00:07:24.069 --> 00:07:27.989 position:50% align:center
Not long from now
I'm holding an exhibition.

00:07:28.073 --> 00:07:30.241 position:50% align:center
You're welcome to come see it.

00:07:36.915 --> 00:07:39.751 position:50% align:center
Well, Leon? Should I go?

00:07:48.802 --> 00:07:52.972 position:50% align:center
Hey, Panic? Are you a boy?

00:07:53.056 --> 00:07:54.808 position:50% align:center
