[RIKA, AI]
Huh?

00:16:23.024 --> 00:16:24.776 position:50% align:center
[NEIRU]
She cleared the game?

00:16:24.859 --> 00:16:25.860 position:50% align:center
[ACCA]
Exactly.

00:16:25.944 --> 00:16:27.320 position:50% align:center
Which means you
need to work hard

00:16:27.404 --> 00:16:30.657 position:50% align:center
so you can follow
in her footsteps.

00:16:30.740 --> 00:16:33.284 position:50% align:center
[RIKA] I guess that kind
of makes Momoe the winner?

00:16:33.368 --> 00:16:34.953 position:50% align:center
She could have told us.

00:16:35.036 --> 00:16:36.496 position:50% align:center
[NEIRU]
Agreed.

00:16:40.709 --> 00:16:42.419 position:50% align:center
Hey. I can't go with you.

00:16:42.502 --> 00:16:44.170 position:50% align:center
I've got stuff to do.

00:16:44.254 --> 00:16:45.839 position:50% align:center
I'll see ya later!

00:16:45.922 --> 00:16:48.008 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
Wait, what kinda stuff?

00:16:48.091 --> 00:16:49.342 position:50% align:center
[NEIRU]
Bye.

00:16:52.178 --> 00:16:53.972 position:50% align:center
Wanna go get some ramen?

00:16:54.055 --> 00:16:55.390 position:50% align:center
Sure.

00:16:56.850 --> 00:16:58.560 position:50% align:center
[AI]
I'm home!

00:17:07.777 --> 00:17:08.945 position:50% align:center
[TAE]
Where are you going?

00:17:09.029 --> 00:17:10.321 position:50% align:center
It's late.

00:17:10.405 --> 00:17:12.657 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Stuff... with everyone.

00:17:12.741 --> 00:17:14.284 position:50% align:center
Everyone?

00:17:15.618 --> 00:17:17.078 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Everyone.

00:17:20.206 --> 00:17:22.459 position:50% align:center
Fine, but please
send me a message

00:17:22.542 --> 00:17:25.045 position:50% align:center
at least every half hour.

00:17:25.128 --> 00:17:27.464 position:50% align:center
[AI]
'Kay. I'm off.

00:17:50.737 --> 00:17:52.113 position:50% align:center
[AI]
It's me?

00:17:52.197 --> 00:17:54.032 position:50% align:center
No, it's different.

00:17:55.158 --> 00:17:56.785 position:50% align:center
[SAWAKI]
It's you.

00:17:56.868 --> 00:18:00.914 position:50% align:center
But when you're all grown up.

00:18:00.997 --> 00:18:03.917 position:50% align:center
[AI]
So, it's like adult me?

00:18:04.000 --> 00:18:05.794 position:50% align:center
Really?

00:18:05.877 --> 00:18:09.506 position:50% align:center
Does this portrait
remind you of anyone?

00:18:13.510 --> 00:18:15.011 position:50% align:center
My mom?

00:18:15.095 --> 00:18:16.888 position:50% align:center
[SAWAKI]
Yes.

00:18:16.971 --> 00:18:18.473 position:50% align:center
In the not-so-distant future,

00:18:18.556 --> 00:18:21.476 position:50% align:center
you'll be a wonderful,
adult woman like your mother.

00:18:21.559 --> 00:18:25.438 position:50% align:center
Kind, strong, and beautiful.

00:18:27.399 --> 00:18:28.900 position:50% align:center
I get it.

00:18:28.983 --> 00:18:30.944 position:50% align:center
You love my mom.

00:18:31.027 --> 00:18:35.156 position:50% align:center
Yes. I do, Ai.

00:18:35.240 --> 00:18:37.283 position:50% align:center
And seeing as
you're her daughter...

00:18:40.078 --> 00:18:42.664 position:50% align:center
...I wish you would have
more faith in yourself.

00:18:45.125 --> 00:18:46.209 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Mister Sawaki.

00:18:46.292 --> 00:18:48.253 position:50% align:center
[SAWAKI]
Yes?

00:18:48.336 --> 00:18:52.090 position:50% align:center
[AI] There's something
I want to ask you.

00:18:54.801 --> 00:18:56.094 position:50% align:center
It's about Koito.

00:18:56.177 --> 00:18:58.179 position:50% align:center
Please tell me why she died.

00:19:01.683 --> 00:19:05.729 position:50% align:center
[ACCA] It seems our plans
may end up going off-course.

00:19:05.812 --> 00:19:07.731 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA]
Looks like it.

00:19:07.814 --> 00:19:09.024 position:50% align:center
[ACCA]
To confront Thanatos,

00:19:09.107 --> 00:19:12.193 position:50% align:center
we need warriors of
Eros, his polar opposite.

00:19:14.362 --> 00:19:17.615 position:50% align:center
Do you think Momoe will
go back there for us?

00:19:17.699 --> 00:19:19.701 position:50% align:center
It's hard to say.

00:19:19.784 --> 00:19:21.870 position:50% align:center
She knows it now.

00:19:21.953 --> 00:19:24.539 position:50% align:center
The overwhelming fear of death.

00:19:35.633 --> 00:19:37.177 position:50% align:center
[HYPHEN]
That's not good.

00:19:37.260 --> 00:19:39.346 position:50% align:center
Might wanna see a doctor.

00:19:40.055 --> 00:19:41.139 position:50% align:center
[HYPHEN]
Congratulations.

00:19:41.222 --> 00:19:43.141 position:50% align:center
You completed your mission.

00:19:43.224 --> 00:19:45.185 position:50% align:center
That girl came back to life.

00:19:45.518 --> 00:19:46.436 position:50% align:center
<i>Veni!</i>

00:19:46.519 --> 00:19:48.229 position:50% align:center
[HYPHEN]
I'd like to let you go.

00:19:48.313 --> 00:19:50.523 position:50% align:center
Out of respect for the way
you've risked your life

00:19:50.607 --> 00:19:52.901 position:50% align:center
for friendship and all that.

00:19:52.984 --> 00:19:57.697 position:50% align:center
The problem is, Frill will get
mad at me if she finds out.

00:19:57.781 --> 00:19:59.199 position:50% align:center
[MOMOE]
Frill?

00:19:59.282 --> 00:20:02.660 position:50% align:center
[HYPHEN] This is a real pain,
so I'll cut to the chase.

00:20:02.744 --> 00:20:04.871 position:50% align:center
Do you want to die here?

00:20:13.254 --> 00:20:15.298 position:50% align:center
Yep. I figured
this would happen.

00:20:24.015 --> 00:20:25.558 position:50% align:center
Panic, no.

00:20:26.976 --> 00:20:28.186 position:50% align:center
[HYPHEN]
In that case,

00:20:28.269 --> 00:20:30.772 position:50% align:center
I'll just have to
settle for this thing.

00:20:36.820 --> 00:20:39.823 position:50% align:center
[HYPHEN] They say crocodile
tastes a lot like chicken.

00:20:47.080 --> 00:20:48.998 position:50% align:center
[HYPHEN]
Here, try some.

00:20:59.217 --> 00:21:00.802 position:50% align:center
[MOMOE'S MOTHER]
Are you all right?

00:21:00.885 --> 00:21:02.429 position:50% align:center
What's wrong?

00:21:09.436 --> 00:21:11.938 position:50% align:center
[MOMOE]
I can't sleep. I can't sleep.

00:21:12.022 --> 00:21:17.402 position:50% align:center
I can't sleep. I can't sleep.
I can't sleep. I can't sleep.

00:21:19.738 --> 00:21:22.657 position:50% align:center
I can't sleep. I can't sleep.

00:22:58.420 --> 00:23:00.005 position:50% align:center
[MOMOE]
